{"tid":1275354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小小意見for文宣","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T19:55:33.000Z","uid":263905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"42d418ab3004f8b34e7d1184cceb48acb3c52298","tid":1275354,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:19:10.000Z","msg":"首先，宜家呢一刻危機都未解除<br />\n好多義士都可能未安全<br />\n大家可以的話各自tg幫得就幫<br />\n感謝<br />\n<br />\n正題<br />\n今日由早上回歸升旗禮果種終極矛盾<br />\n直至衝緊果種同狗一門之隔既緊張<br />\n直到衝左入去見到一隻狗都無既懸疑<br />\n然後撤退時真正體現一個都不能少果個高潮<br />\n果種感動<br />\n直頭好睇過endgame<br />\n<br />\n我相信如果可以將所有片，相，報道<br />\n有哂source咁整合<br />\n成為一個紀錄<br />\n再好似上次咁<br />\n翻譯成多國語言<br />\n聯絡外媒etc<br />\n個迴響應該好大<br />\n<br />\n我真心覺得<br />\n今日各方手足<br />\n無論喺前定後<br />\n內定外<br />\n加上記者<br />\n議員<br />\n都值得好好表揚<br />\n<br />\n啲仆街一定會用破壞立法會破壞社會安寧呢啲on9野<br />\n攻擊今日付出既各位手足<br />\n所以要喺宣傳上反擊<br />\n可以參考翻太陽花<br />\n好似打得甩無罪<br />\n<br />\n希望可以出分力<br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"2619caec5cedf4cb5eba38786b9ded5128d016b5","tid":1275354,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:27:41.000Z","msg":"推呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87854f3312e09ab4a1bd46b3ecc489d626246153","tid":1275354,"uid":103353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:33:48.000Z","msg":"仲有一齊走之前<br />\n<br />\n有條片留守既接受訪問<br />\n<br />\n講解預左為香港付出"},{"pid":"fc404138ccd764c42ee4b1ca33f84ff13e393fcf","tid":1275354,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:42:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4cd47f53e9462f28a9bd2f010f14aa173126c2c7","tid":1275354,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:42:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3a9a973c3d293620185f473c13bb76217f032d04","tid":1275354,"